donor_name: UNITED NATIONS DEVELOPMENT FUND FOR WOME
outputs.output_descr: The programme will focus on three major intervention areas, these are: (i) creating an enabling environment (developing and implementing the LED Strategies, cluster development guidelines,  PPDF and others); (ii) developing capacities of the key economic institutions; and (iii) targeted catalytic interventions, these are: Business Cluster Development, setting up and/or strengthening BDRCs, competitive LED Funds for inclusive micro-finance in 27 cities.
